Download Apache Hadoop - latest version .. !! (Apache website)
Unzip the file to C directory ( -> since it has the admin priviliges )

Add the environmental variable - HADOOP_HOME -> upto the bin directory.

Also make sure that JAVA 1.8 is installed 

Add JAVA_HOME user variable -> in the bin

Edit the following file in etc/hadoop folder 

core-site.xml

<configuration>
   <property>
       <name>fs.defaultFS</name>
       <value>hdfs://localhost:9000</value>
   </property>
</configuration>


